Rajoy to Ask Merkel for More ECB Help for Spain, Expansion Says

-- B y   A n g e l i n e   B e n o i t
-- 
2011-12-07T08:06:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-07/rajoy-to-ask-merkel-for-more-ecb-help-for-spain-expansion-says.html
  Spain ’s People’s Party’s leader and
Prime Minister-elect  Mariano Rajoy  will ask German Chancellor
 Angela Merkel  at a meeting in Marseille,  France , on Dec. 8 to
support the  European Central Bank ’s purchase of more Spanish
debt on the secondary market in exchange for steeper budget
cuts,  Expansion  reported, citing unidentified members of the
party.  Rajoy is due to take over from the ruling Socialists on
Dec. 21.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Angeline Benoit in Madrid  at 
 abenoit4@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Craig Stirling at 
 cstirling1@bloomberg.net  